# Emotion Classifier

## What it does
This program uses Hugging Face's pretrained model
[`j-hartmann/emotion-english-distilroberta-base`](https://huggingface.co/j-hartmann/emotion-english-distilroberta-base)
to classify text into emotions like joy, sadness, anger, fear, disgust, and neutral.

## How to run
1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install transformers torch
